OL,3,CScotland drug deaths dropped last
OL,4,Cyear, but the crisis is far from over
OL,6,FThe publication of Scotland's latest
OL,7,Fdrug death statistics is an annual
OL,8,Fevent that has become tragically
OL,9,Froutine.
OL,11,FThousands more families left grieving
OL,12,F- yet again - and another drugs
OL,13,Fminister put in front of the cameras
OL,14,Fto offer apologies and promises.
OL,16,FMaree Todd is the fifth minister with
OL,17,Fthis responsibility in five years.
OL,19,F"I'm desperately sorry," Todd said,
OL,20,Fbefore promising her government is
OL,21,Fdoing everything it can to tackle this.
