OL,3,CScotland drug deaths dropped last
OL,4,Cyear, but the crisis is far from over
OL,6,FThe latest figures show 1,017 deaths
OL,7,Ffor last year. This is actually down
OL,8,F13% and is the lowest number of
OL,9,Ffatalities recorded since 2017.
OL,11,FBut the drugs minister admits this is
OL,12,Fnot cause for joy or celebration.
OL,14,FThere was a dip two years ago, and the
OL,15,Fdrugs minister at that time, Elena
OL,16,FWhitham, announced the Scottish
OL,17,Fgovernment was turning a corner.
OL,19,FThat was followed by a 12% rise last
OL,20,Fyear.
