OL,3,CScotland drug deaths dropped last
OL,4,Cyear, but the crisis is far from over
OL,6,FEarly forecasts based on suspected
OL,7,Fdrug deaths in the first half of this
OL,8,Fyear suggest the next drug deaths
OL,9,Freport will show another rise.
OL,11,FThe trend appears to be that the
OL,12,Fnumber of people dying in Scotland
OL,13,Frose to an unprecedented level from
OL,14,Fabout 2015 to 2022.
OL,16,FSince then - despite tens of millions
OL,17,Fof pounds thrown at the problem - the
OL,18,Fnumbers are staying worryingly high,
OL,19,Fand Scotland remains the drug death
OL,20,Fcapital of Europe.
