OL,11,FThis is reflected in the toxicology
OL,12,Freports of those who died, showing the
OL,13,Fprevalence of various drugs, including
OL,14,Fheroin, methadone, benzodiazepines,
OL,15,Fcocaine, and etizolam.
OL,17,FThese are often combined with alcohol,
OL,18,Fcreating a deadly cocktail that causes
OL,19,Fthe body's organs to shut down.
