OL,3,CScotland drug deaths dropped last
OL,4,Cyear, but the crisis is far from over
OL,6,FThere's also the new terror of
OL,7,Fnitazines emerging on the streets -
OL,8,Fthey're a kind of synthetic opioid not
OL,9,Fdissimilar to fentanyl that swept
OL,10,Facross America with devastating effect.
OL,12,FThe Scottish government has taken some
OL,13,Fbold steps to turn this crisis around.
OL,15,FIn Glasgow, the UK's first ever drug
OL,16,Fconsumption room was opened earlier
OL,17,Fthis year.
