OL,3,CScotland drug deaths dropped last
OL,4,Cyear, but the crisis is far from over
OL,6,FThere are now plans to expand this
OL,7,Fservice to have a drug consumption
OL,8,Froom in Edinburgh as well.
OL,10,FThe forecasts of another rise in drug
OL,11,Fdeaths next year show how much the
OL,12,FScottish government is now swimming
OL,13,Fagainst the tide.
OL,15,FHaving watched the numbers escalate to
OL,16,Fsuch a high level on their watch,
OL,17,Fthey're struggling to get it back
OL,18,Funder control.
